@vrothberg 

> I begin to think we should address the issue on Buildah's side. We somehow regressed but for good reasons. We could improve the error message (and docs?) to better communicate what's happening.

I agree (since the theoretical usecase of these safe resolution tools is more for container runtimes operating on a container rootfs than the whole "build context" concept from `docker build`), but feel free to ping me if you want my input.
